        {
            "title": "香港2025年出生人數下降 人口壓力料將加劇",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Census and Statistics Department\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"603\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/bu8.mE6P0ii8YmgzTFvGCg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwMztjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/0f5e6703b605da2bb1708fab3b5eb9f0\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"><span>Census and Statistics Department</span></figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 香港面臨遏制出生人口下降的難題，而與此同時該市的人口老齡化迅速。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據《南華早報》引述香港政務司副司長卓永興的辦公室消息報導，去年香港登記新生兒共計31714人，比2024年下降14%。這一數字比2022年疫情時的前低點還要低低3%。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"603\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/zC9Fc4U9xePqiy2RYgzipw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwMztjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/57293d60897f947d09f1e11802b4ab4e\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">新生兒數量的驟降終結了此前連續兩年的成長趨勢，對官方為解決香港低出生率問題所做的努力造成打擊，低出生率是東亞地區政府面臨的一個普遍挑戰。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著越來越多的人退出勞動力群體，這一下降趨勢也將加劇香港的人口壓力，當地是世界上人口老齡化速度最快的城市之一。政府預計到2039年，65歲及以上居民將占總人口的31%，高於2021年的20%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2a042523-77d9-361f-a580-7d4e5057bd4d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">卓永興的辦公室未立即回覆置評請求。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Hong Kong’s Plunging Births Risk Worsening Demographic Pressure</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF2025%E5%B9%B4%E5%87%BA%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8%E4%B8%8B%E9%99%8D-%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%A3%93%E5%8A%9B%E6%96%99%E5%B0%87%E5%8A%A0%E5%8A%87-065429536.html",
