            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "日本5年期國債標售吸引的需求弱於12個月均值 政治風險抑制投資者情緒",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 日本5年期國債拍賣吸引的需求弱於過去12個月平均水平，政治風險加劇抑制了投資者的購買意願。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">投標倍數為3.08，而12月上次發行時為3.17，12個月平均值為3.54。拍賣結果公佈後，債券期貨價格下跌。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日本首相據報導計畫提前舉行大選，這促使「高市交易」捲土重來，日圓和日債雙雙下挫。5年期國債殖利率已升至1.615%，為2000年該品種首次發行以來的最高水平。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/3vhAbGAulWWvuQ2JMycSSQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/0cadab93250d32245df1b8c1ee5512d8\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">投資者正密切關注財政風險，因為解散眾議院可能會鞏固自民黨的執政地位，並為更多刺激措施鋪平道路。日圓兌美元匯率跌至2024年7月以來的最低水平後，日本央行提前加息的可能性也在上升。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d3ce369e-fea5-3616-82e0-c6aeb117c2d4-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Japan’s Five-Year Bond Sale Demand Weaker Than 12-Month Average</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC5%E5%B9%B4%E6%9C%9F%E5%9C%8B%E5%82%B5%E6%A8%99%E5%94%AE%E5%90%B8%E5%BC%95%E7%9A%84%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E5%BC%B1%E6%96%BC12%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E5%9D%87%E5%80%BC-%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA%E6%8A%91%E5%88%B6%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E8%80%85%E6%83%85%E7%B7%92-041839897.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-14 13:50:53",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "比特幣升至兩個月高點 受宏觀利好因素推動",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 比特幣觸及兩個月高點，1月份延續謹慎走高行情，地緣政治不確定性增強了其吸引力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周三早盤，比特幣在新加坡市場一度漲2.4%至96,348美元，創11月16日以來盤中最高水平。第二大代幣以太幣一度飆升5.1%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">比特幣2025年以低迷態勢收官，全年累計跌幅逾6%，交易區間狹窄。但1月該代幣顯露出了潛在突破跡象，交易員認為它有可能在資產類別競爭中占據優勢。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「中期來看，我認為我們可能會看到投資者基於追趕黃金的敘事將更多資金配置到比特幣上，其他風險資產的表現也十分亮眼，」 Arctic Digital研究主管Justin d’Anethan表示。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-0b85391f-296c-3994-9275-f212382609a8-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/369E3QTB4sMVUD0d4HnkGg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/c7c849a89c7101a98117316a5eb26c52\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Kronos Research首席投資官Vincent Liu指出，另一個因素是比特幣衍生品市場出現軋空現象。CoinGlass的數據顯示，過去24小時內約有2.7億美元的比特幣空頭頭寸被平倉。而在整個加密貨幣市場，約有6億美元的空頭頭寸被平倉。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">FalconX全球市場聯席主管Joshua Lim稱，總體而言，交易員認為當前宏觀環境對比特幣有利。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Bitcoin Climbs to Two-Month High of $96,000 on Macro Tailwinds</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AF%94%E7%89%B9%E5%B9%A3%E5%8D%87%E8%87%B3%E5%85%A9%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E9%AB%98%E9%BB%9E-%E5%8F%97%E5%AE%8F%E8%A7%80%E5%88%A9%E5%A5%BD%E5%9B%A0%E7%B4%A0%E6%8E%A8%E5%8B%95-040017750.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-14 12:35:57",
