            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"特朗普稱摩通CEO對司法部調查聯儲局的批評是「錯誤的」\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/mRtDQwzjYF740ZWDQygECA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/8b6d8840-f0ba-11f0-8bf9-ac4d3d35acf6\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">特朗普稱摩通CEO對司法部調查聯儲局的批評是「錯誤的」</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
